  <steps>
    <Step id="c009b2f4-c3f0-4a68-b81e-9ba442faa8b3" name="Introduction" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt;The number of sample points required for your assessment and monitoring is based on three variables:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='20'&gt;1&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='20'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#0000ff'&gt;&lt;b&gt;. &lt;u&gt;&lt;a target='_blank' href='asfunction:GotoStep,dce263d3-39e3-4ca2-9391-ef982e73f98a'&gt;Resources&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt; (time and funding) available for monitoring.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt;2.&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Degree of &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#0000ff'&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a target='_blank' href='asfunction:GotoStep,dce263d3-39e3-4ca2-9391-ef982e73f98a'&gt;risk or sensitivity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt; associated with the project.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt;3.&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;The amount of &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#0000ff'&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a target='_blank' href='asfunction:GotoStep,dce263d3-39e3-4ca2-9391-ef982e73f98a'&gt;variability&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt; within the unit being sampled.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" intro="true">
