    <Step id="a6586f37-79dd-4b80-8087-5b03464494be" name="Examples of Sample-size" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color='#000000'&gt;Often decisions on how many sample points you monitor are determined by resources (time and money). However, some areas may be particularly prone to land management impacts and this may lead you to increasing your confidence level and subsequently sample size. Conversely, for low-risk sites with little unit variability and impacts, the number of sample points could be less. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
